race.comment: BOLTED IN (6) is ticking along nicely without winning, only beaten a lip last time at Oakbank over this trip. Crowther sticks and a repeat effort here looks good enough to get the job done. TRIPOD TERROR (2) has been solid since returning, without having a win to show for it. Peak fitness now and should relish the rise in trip. Watch for him bursting through. EXALTED KATE (7) improved sharply at the latest when making light work of her rivals at Penola. Genuine hope if she holds that form. AMBELLO (8) doesn't win out of turn but was a flashing light late last time at Mt Gambier. Gets the chance to settle closer and gets a key booking in Holder. Don't underestimate.
